title: Bug 116609[Regression]Color orange doesn't work.
description: Bug 116609[Regression]Color orange doesn't work. Description: Color orange doesn't work.
OB: When setting the color or background color to orange for a report item, the color does not change to orange.
EB: When setting the color or background color to orange for a report item, the color should change to orange.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Insert a report item.
2. Set the color or background color to orange.
